# Blog page: fetch Instagram posts (optional).
# Get a Page Access Token from Meta for Developers and connect your Instagram Business/Creator account to a Facebook Page.
# Then set either (A) or (B):
# (A) Instagram Business Account ID + token:
# INSTAGRAM_IG_USER_ID=123456789
# INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_page_access_token
# (B) Facebook Page ID + token (we resolve the IG account from the page):
# INSTAGRAM_PAGE_ID=123456789
# INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_page_access_token
